item.description:
The project follows a successful Git branching model, utilizing several key branches. Among them are:
origin/master: This is the primary branch, where the HEAD always represents a production-ready version of the source code.
origin/develop This serves as the main branch for ongoing development. The HEAD here reflects the latest implemented changes intended for the upcoming release. It is often referred to as the &ldquo;integration branch.&rdquo;
